import React from "react";
import { Container, Row, Col, Card } from "react-bootstrap";
import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css";

const GridLayout = () => {
  return (
    <Container fluid className="full-height-container">
      <Row className="full-height-row">
        <Col md={4} className="full-height-col mb-4">
          <Card className="w-100">
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Column 1</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>Content for column 1.</Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
        <Col md={4} className="full-height-col mb-4">
          <Card className="w-100">
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Column 2</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>Content for column 2.</Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
        <Col md={4} className="full-height-col mb-4">
          <Card className="w-100">
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Column 3</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>Content for column 3.</Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
      </Row>
      <Row className="full-height-row">
        <Col md={4} className="full-height-col mb-4">
          <Card className="w-100">
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Column 4</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>Content for column 4.</Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
        <Col md={4} className="full-height-col mb-4">
          <Card className="w-100">
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Column 5</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>Content for column 5.</Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
        <Col md={4} className="full-height-col mb-4">
          <Card className="w-100">
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Column 6</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>Content for column 6.</Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default GridLayout;
